  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Regulated negative pressure-assisted wound therapy (RNPT) is regarded as a gold standard
      technology for treatment of various chronic and acute wounds. The investigators plan to
      evaluate the efficacy and ease of use of this device.
    </textblock>
